title: Wippich Media Library
description:
Wippich Media Library is intended to help you to index files or folders that contain subject matter which doesn't fit neatly into a single category.

I do not sell software.  The concepts I'm studying at Univesity do not fit neatly into one category; therefore, directories are inadequate.

Setup:
Extract the contents of WML.zip into a folder.  If you have trouble getting the program to run, extract to the root of an external hard drive or ram drive. This software was made to run on Windows XP.
